# Analyst Summary Template

# This file is a Jinja2 template for generating the analyst summary in Markdown format.

# Incident Summary
## Incident ID: {{ incident.id }}
### Severity: {{ incident.severity }}
### Tags: {{ incident.tags | join(', ') }}

---

### Incident Details
- **Description:** {{ incident.description }}
- **Timestamp:** {{ incident.timestamp }}
- **Source:** {{ incident.source }}

### Indicators of Compromise (IOCs)
| Type       | Value               | Enrichment          |
|------------|---------------------|---------------------|
{% for indicator in incident.iocs %}
| {{ indicator.type }} | {{ indicator.value }} | {{ indicator.enrichment }} |
{% endfor %}

### Actions Taken
- **Isolation Status:** {{ incident.isolation_status }}
- **Notes:** {{ incident.notes }}

---

### Additional Information
- **MITRE ATT&CK Techniques:** {{ incident.mitre_techniques | join(', ') }}